SQL_STMT_U.val: select row_number() OVER (ORDER BY T0.DocEntry desc) as 'No' , T0.CardName as 'Distributor' , T0.NumAtCard as 'No.TRO' , T0.DocNum as 'No.Faktur' , T0.DocDate as 'Tgl.Penerimaan' , T0.IgloLineTotal as 'Jml.Harga' , T0.DiscSum as 'Jml.Diskon' , T0.VatSum as 'Jml.PPN' , T0.DocTotal as 'Nilai Faktur' , T0.DocStatus as 'Status' , T0.BaseType as 'Base Type' , T0.ObjType as 'Object Type' from OPDN T0 where (T0.CardName like '%'+ISNULL(':2','')+'%') and (T0.DocStatus = ':3' or ':3' is null or ':3' = '') and (T0.DocDate between ':4' and ':5') :8 and T0.datasource = 'S' and T0.DocNum like '%'+ISNULL(':1','')+'%' and T0.U_IDU_Kode_PT like ':6' and T0.canceled <> 'C' and (T0.canceled = ':7' or ':7' is null or ':7' = '') :9 :10 :11 order by T0.docentry desc

SQL_STMT_U.val: select row_number() OVER (ORDER BY T0.DocEntry desc) as 'No' , T0.CardName as 'Distributor' , T0.NumAtCard as 'No.TRO' , T0.DocNum as 'No.Faktur' , T0.DocDate as 'Tgl.Penerimaan' , T1.LineTotal as 'Jml.Harga' , T2.total_discount as 'Jml.Diskon' , T1.VatSum as 'Jml.PPN' , T0.DocTotal as 'Nilai Faktur' , T0.DocStatus as 'Status' , T1.BaseType as 'Base Type' , T0.ObjType as 'Object Type' from OPDN T0 join PDN1 T1 on T0.DocEntry=T1.DocEntry left join GRN_H T2 on T0.NumAtCard = T2.name where (T0.CardName like '%'+ISNULL(':2','')+'%') and (T0.DocStatus = ':3' or ':3' is null or ':3' = '') and (T0.DocDate between ':4' and ':5') and T0.datasource = 'S' and T0.DocNum like '%'+ISNULL(':1','')+'%' and T0.U_IDU_Kode_PT like ':6' and T0.canceled <> 'C' and (T0.canceled = ':7' or ':7' is null or ':7' = '') order by T0.docentry desc

SQL_STMT_U.val: select T0.DocDate as 'Posting Date' , T0.DocNum as 'Document Number' , T0.CardName as 'Supplier Name' , TRIM(REPLACE(T0.numatcard,char(59),'')) as 'Supplier Reference' , T0.U_IDU_Kode_PT as 'Consignee' , T0.AuthCode as 'BL Number' , T1.Dscription as 'Item Name' , T1.OpenQty as 'Open Qty' , T1.U_IDU_QtyPack as 'Qty Pack' , T1.U_IDU_UOMPack as 'UOM Pack' , T1.Quantity as 'Qty' , T2.UomName as 'UOM Qty' , T1.WhsCode as 'Warehouse' , T1.PriceBefDi as 'Price Before Discount' , T1.DiscPrcnt as 'Discount' , T1.Price as 'Price' , T1.VatSum as 'PPN' , T0.DocCur as 'Currency' , T1.LineTotal as 'SubTotal' , T0.doctotal as 'Total' , Trim(REPLACE(REPLACE(REPLACE(T0.comments,char(13),' '),char(10),' '),Char(59),' ')) as 'Remarks' , T0.DocStatus as 'Status' , T1.baseref as 'Base Number' , T1.BaseType as 'Base Type' , T0.ObjType as 'Object Type' from OPDN T0 join PDN1 T1 on T0.DocEntry=T1.DocEntry JOIN OUOM T2 on T1.UomCode = T2.UomCode where (T0.CardCode = ':2' or ':2' is null or ':2' = '') and (T0.DocStatus = ':3' or ':3' is null or ':3' = '') and (T0.DocDate between ':4' and ':5') :8 and T0.datasource = 'S' and T0.DocNum like '%'+ISNULL(':1','')+'%' and T0.U_IDU_Kode_PT like ':6' and T0.canceled <> 'C' and (T0.canceled = ':7' or ':7' is null or ':7' = '') :9 :10 :11 order by T0.docentry desc
